OOC: Okay, now i'm back for good. Jeremiah that is.
Sorry Jen, I thought it was Element, but let's just continue, but it 
will be hard to squash him into the ground with your foot when he's 
flying :)


BIC:

Tantrum franticly dove out of the way to avoid the missile, but since 
they were mentally guided, one of them hit, setting off the other, in 
a large explosion, sending Tantrum flying miles away, landing him near 
G1 Rampage. He looked up at him through pained eyes, and a furious 
snort. The damage he had taken from Lavatrons kick finally caught up 
with him, and his chest armor was ripped and burnt thanks to the 
carefully placed missile, "Ghhnn, let'sss get ...." his computer 
finished the sentence for him. "Unit Tantrum seriously damaged, return 
to base" it hummed. Tantrum went limp.
